did.head: DESCRIPTIVE SUMMARY
did.unittitle: International Brotherhood of Pulp, Sulphite and Paper Mill Workers Records on Microfilm, 1906-1957

origination.label: Creator:
origination.corpname: International Brotherhood of Pulp, Sulphite and Paper Mill Workers

did.repository: Kheel Center for Labor-Management Documentation and Archives, Cornell University Library
did.abstract: These papers of the IBPSPMW cover most of the years from 1906, the year of the organization of the International Brotherhood, to 1957. Files for a few years are missing.

scopecontent.head: COLLECTION DESCRIPTION
scopecontent.p: Microfilm copies of the files of the International Brotherhood of Pulp, Sulphite, and Paper Mill Workers.
This collection consists primarily of the President-Secretary's files.
